            android:layout_width="wrap_content"
            android:layout_height="wrap_content"
            android:layout_marginBottom="10dp"
            android:text="IIEST(erstwhile B.E.College) is a premiere engineering Institute(lately designated as the 32nd NIT) of india with NIRF rank of 21 among all engineering institutions of india and 6 among Architecture Institutes.IIEST is not just an engineering college, it's literally an emotion. The environment here has the magic to transform all your anxiety and problems into happiness. It not only gives us the degree oriented education, but gives us the exposure to explore, and to be a true human BEing."
